id: auth-fixture
name: Skill Human Name
version: 1.0.0
category: test-authoring
archetype: domain-expert
description: |
  One paragraph. What this skill does and when Claude should load it.
  Written for the ROUTING layer — answer: "when should I invoke this skill?"
  NOT for the user — that's SKILL.md's job.
  Keep under 5 sentences.
